## ⧖ Validação Antes de Push

```bash
# Frontend
fnm exec --using v22.22.2 pnpm check
fnm exec --using v22.22.2 pnpm build

# Backend
node --check backend/src/server.js
node --test backend/src/services/ledger.test.js

# Tudo junto
make check
make build
```

